  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-12）：蚂蚁集团 LLaDA2.0，WSD 策略+多并行优化，撑起 100B 扩散语言模型",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500877&idx=1&sn=36a181eca5dc433b98e99be008c4cdbe",
  "date": "2025-12-12 09:43:00",
