  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：LLaDA2.0-mini</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.48518518518518516\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"564\" data-imgfileid=\"100017214\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b919362&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwicdE5SVwfjC2E8VeCnZuUxOsY6AagyCRBMhltryQAic5bMDqrc0Z8Yn89bwdldcoOjuBhFF2kgU0g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LLaDA2.0-mini 是一种扩散语言模型，采用16BA1B混合专家（MoE）架构。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">作为LLaDA系列的增强版，经过指令调优，优化用于实际应用。该模型在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">代码生成和复杂数学推理</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">等任务中表现出色，展示了强大的推理能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/llada2-0-mini\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/llada2-0-mini</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Shisa V2.1&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"648\" data-imgfileid=\"100017211\" data-ratio=\"0.5564814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9a4a511f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwicdE5SVwfjC2E8VeCnZuUxV28bI8DuUkxw12mXniakEqEd7xVibl2VcGXprClA36EobwtAyeAqXgUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Shisa V2.1 是 Shisa.AI 开发的双语日语和英语通用聊天模型的更新版本。该模型旨在提升日语任务的表现，同时保持强大的英语能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过重新采样 Shisa V2 数据集并进行数据修正，Shisa V2.1 在指令跟随、翻译、礼貌性和其他日语特定语言改进方面取得了显著提升。新版本包括改进的 14B 和 70B 类模型，以及适用于本地和边缘使用的 1.2B、3B 和 8B 新模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/shisa-v2-1\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/shisa-v2-1</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：FeRA</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"516\" data-imgfileid=\"100017213\" data-ratio=\"0.4444444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=49b51820&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwicdE5SVwfjC2E8VeCnZuUxth8BKMkwENzYCs9KQZjcQOoVF3h1UicVXiacdC9A7oP6AicCIdZ0am81A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★FeRA项目旨在通过频率-能量约束路由优化来实现有效的扩散适应微调。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了一种新的方法来提高扩散模型的适应性和性能，特别是在图像生成任务中。通过引入FeRAConfig和FeRAModel，用户可以在PyTorch环境中轻松实现模型的训练和优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fera\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fera</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">banana-slides</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"768\" data-imgfileid=\"100017212\" data-ratio=\"0.6601851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0949a283&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwicdE5SVwfjC2E8VeCnZuUx7XnrAWrc6vLuoFNja7XvPSl3T16WSemSeicQLbvLuDlqibnCGJ9vicnoA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★banana-slides 是一个基于 nano banana pro 的原生 AI PPT 生成应用，旨在降低 PPT 制作门槛。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">用户可以通过上传任意模板图片和素材，利用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">智能解析功能</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">生成 PPT。项目支持通过一句话、大纲或页面描述自动生成 PPT，并允许用户通过自然语言进行口头修改和一键导出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/banana-slides\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/banana-slides</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：OneThinker</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"564\" data-imgfileid=\"100017215\" data-ratio=\"0.4842592592592593\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0a7254fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwicdE5SVwfjC2E8VeCnZuUxxotr5Wq0J5YBWpuoHXibmvm2bviboVaUXS4TU1HAUmh8Bh8A2a1tDb6g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★OneThinker是一个多模态推理模型，能够在单一模型中处理多种基础</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">视觉任务。项目构建了大规模的OneThinker-600k多任务训练语料库，并通过高质量的CoT注释构建了OneThinker-SFT-340k。此外，项目提出了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">EMA-GRPO</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，一种新的强化学习方法，通过跟踪任务奖励标准差的移动平均来平衡不同视觉任务的异构奖励信号。OneThinker在31个基准测试中表现出色，展示了跨任务知识转移和零样本泛化的潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/onethinker\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/onethinker</a> &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">⚙️ Robotics 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：IR-SIM</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"416\" data-imgfileid=\"100017216\" data-ratio=\"0.35833333333333334\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7187ec0d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwicdE5SVwfjC2E8VeCnZuUxLhImg8V1gibIdWRX6JbwvN3VdBAyrCicEwTHhLdD0JZ7Jd67ZLBmicHIA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★IR-SIM是一个开源的、基于Python的轻量级机器人模拟器，专为导航、控制和强化学习而设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它提供了一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">简单、用户友好</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的框架，内置</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">碰撞检测功能</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，用于建模机器人、传感器和环境。IR-SIM非常适合学术和教育用途，能够在自定义场景中快速原型化机器人和学习算法，所需的编码和硬件要求极少。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ir-sim\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ir-sim</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总并简要介绍了六个最新的 AI 项目，涵盖扩散语言模型、多语言聊天模型、扩散适应微调框架、AI PPT 生成应用、多模态推理模型和轻量级机器人模拟器。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总并简要介绍了六个最新的 AI 项目，涵盖扩散语言模型、多语言聊天模型、扩散适应微调框架、AI PPT 生成应用、多模态推理模型和轻量级机器人模拟器。",
  "summary": "文章以“今日开源”的形式，快速介绍了当日发布的六个最新 AI 项目。其中包括了蚂蚁集团的 LLaDA2.0-mini 扩散语言模型，以及 Shisa V2.1 双语通用聊天模型。框架工具方面，提到了用于扩散模型微调的 FeRA 项目和原生 AI PPT 生成应用 banana-slides。此外，还介绍了多模态推理模型 OneThinker 和轻量级机器人模拟器 IR-SIM。文章对每个项目进行了简要的功能介绍和突出特点说明，并提供了项目收藏链接，旨在提供最新 AI 技术动态的速览。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "LLaDA2.0-mini 作为扩散语言模型，在代码生成和数学推理方面表现突出。",
      "explanation": "该模型采用 MoE 架构，是 LLaDA 系列针对实际应用优化的增强版，展现了强大的复杂任务处理能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Shisa V2.1 提升了日语任务表现，并拓展了模型规模以适应不同部署需求。",
      "explanation": "作为双语聊天模型的更新版本，通过数据修正和重新采样，显著改善了日语指令遵循和翻译能力，提供了多种规模模型便于本地及边缘部署。"
    },
